# GlamGo тАФ Phase 4B: Platform Gallery & Discovery

> **Purpose:** Build the core in-app experience тАФ the gallery where users browse hairstyles, view style details, and discover stylists.
> This is the HOOK. If the gallery doesn't feel premium, users won't book.
> **Depends on:** Phase 2 (hairstyles seeded) + Phase 3 (auth working)
> **Estimated Time:** ~4 hours

---

## Phase 4B.1: Gallery Page Foundation
**Owner:** Product Engineer (Beloved)
**Time:** ~30 minutes
**Depends on:** Nothing тАФ this is the foundation of the gallery

| # | Task | Details |
| --- | --- | --- |
| 4B.1.1 | Create gallery page layout | `src/app/gallery/page.tsx` тАФ Server Component that fetches hairstyles from Supabase |
| 4B.1.2 | Create gallery module styles | `src/app/gallery/gallery.module.css` тАФ dark luxury aesthetic matching landing page |
| 4B.1.3 | Add page metadata | Title: "Hairstyle Gallery | GlamGo", description for SEO |

**тЬЕ 4B.1 Done = Gallery page renders with Supabase connection, matches design system**

