## Commit Strategy

One commit per logical unit:

1. `feat(gallery): add gallery page foundation and hero`
2. `feat(gallery): add category filter with URL params`
3. `feat(gallery): add hairstyle card and grid components`
4. `feat(gallery): wire up data fetching and filtering`
5. `feat(styles): add style detail page with image gallery`
6. `feat(styles): add style info and stylist list`
7. `feat(stylists): add stylist card component`
8. `feat(stylists): add stylist profile page with header`
9. `feat(stylists): add portfolio and reviews sections`
10. `feat(stylists): add styles offered section`
11. `feat(api): add stylists endpoint with filters`

