## Design Requirements (Apply to All Components)

| Token | Value | Usage |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Background | `#0A0A0F` | Page backgrounds |
| Surface | `rgba(255,255,255,0.03)` | Cards, containers |
| Border | `rgba(255,255,255,0.08)` | Card borders, dividers |
| Gold Accent | `#C9A96E` | CTAs, highlights, badges |
| Text Primary | `#FAFAFA` | Headings |
| Text Secondary | `rgba(255,255,255,0.7)` | Body text |
| Text Muted | `rgba(255,255,255,0.4)` | Captions, metadata |
| Font Display | Playfair Display | Headings |
| Font Body | DM Sans | Body, UI |

---

## Database Queries Reference

**Hairstyles with category filter:**
```sql
SELECT * FROM hairstyles 
WHERE ($1::hairstyle_category IS NULL OR category = $1)
ORDER BY is_trending DESC, name ASC;
```

**Stylists for a style:**
```sql
SELECT sp.*, u.full_name, u.avatar_url, ss.stylist_price
FROM stylist_styles ss
JOIN stylist_profiles sp ON ss.stylist_id = sp.id
JOIN users u ON sp.user_id = u.id
WHERE ss.hairstyle_id = $1 AND sp.is_available = true
ORDER BY sp.average_rating DESC;
```

**Stylist profile with user data:**
```sql
SELECT sp.*, u.full_name, u.avatar_url, u.city, u.area
FROM stylist_profiles sp
JOIN users u ON sp.user_id = u.id
WHERE sp.id = $1;
```

